A few things:
- We should use proper class description for native classes. This is mainly for the developer experience, because all classes are logged as "HyperloopClass" right now, instead of printing the actual class behind the wrapper. This PR will replace {{<HyperloopClass: 0x608000072c80>}} with {{<NSMutableArray: 0x608000072c80>}}
- Internal logs should be removed from public log level, e.g. {{\[HYPERLOOP\] didStartNewContext <KrollContext: 0x608000074140>}}. They do not have any value for a Titanium developer
